      },
      "value": {
        "en": [
          "A rectangular base, on which stood a funerary vessel, probably a loutrophoros. The reliefs are framed by a narrow plinth below the figures and a molding, consisting of taenia above ovolo, above the reliefs. A coarsely worked narrow rectangular element below the base would have socketed the monument into the ground."
